column5: Hey yall,  So I decided to hit the creek today and had some decent success (for a newbie ) lol.  I went 2 for 3 loosing what would have been my first brown. All fish were released
Right on... I'm so jealous that you guys are still catching! Maybe next time you'll get that Brown
haha dont be jealous im sure youve got wayy better fishing up in north bay than down here
Well done Mike, just rewards for all the time you're putting in - we'll have to name that pool after you soon
haha yea its defiantly treated me the best out of all the spots on that stretch of river.  Went out again today and only got 1, nice size though around the size of the one I lost that 1 day.
nice shootin !!!! the loses make the rewards that much sweeter...
Nice fish..  The background is awesome
